features of  Online Food Ordering System :


Add food items to menu.
Display menu.
Search food by name.
Place an order.
Add multiple items to cart.
Remove item from cart.
Show total bill.
Apply discount code.
Track order status (ordered, preparing, delivered).
Cancel order.
Show order history.
Display top-selling items.
Sort menu by price.
Sort menu by popularity.
Manage restaurant list.
Select restaurant before ordering.
Estimate delivery time.
Generate invoice.
Rate food after delivery.
Exit with daily sales summary.
